== Rails3 Twitter

The Twitter Mashup Application Sample Made by Ruby on Rails 3.0.3

== Installation

$ git clone git://github.com/mitukiii/rails3-twitter.git
$ cd rails3-twitter
$ bundle install

Rewirte consumer key and consumer secret in app/controllers/application_controller.rb

$ rails server

